------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|R4M6K5S[.sup]|3400-3500   |3800-4000   |0.15        |66.5-68.5   |635         | 
|*[/]     |            |            |            |            |            | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|R4M6K5S     |3300-3400   |3700-3 800  |0.10-0.15   |65-66       |630         | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
